How to Use BioEdge™

Breathe freely – without inhalers, cough syrup, or side effects

Preparation

KeepBioEdge™handy when your breathing feels heavy or blocked (e.g., in the morning after waking up, before bedtime, or during shortness of breath).

Application

Place 1-2 drops ofBioEdge™under the tongue or mix them in a small glass of water. Do this slowly so that the natural active ingredients are optimally absorbed and can exert their effect in the airways.

Repeat & Feel The Effect

UseBioEdge™1-2 × daily, depending on the severity of your symptoms.

Most users notice an improvement within 5 minutes.

For best results – use daily for at least 7 days.

Frequently Asked Questions:

How Quickly Will I Notice Results?

Many users notice an improvement in breathing after just a few days – less coughing and more air. For sustainable regeneration, it is recommended to use the product daily for at least 3-4 weeks.

Is Daily Use Safe?

Yes, the formula is 100% natural and contains no addictive or harmful substances. You can use it several times a day without worry.

Can I Combine It With My Current Medications Or My Inhaler?

In most cases – yes. The product works as a supplement and supports your breathing. If in doubt, however, you should consult your doctor.

Does It Also Help With Chronic Conditions Such As Asthma Or COPD?

Yes, many users with asthma, bronchitis, or COPD report noticeable relief, less shortness of breath, and more air.

How Exactly Do I Use It?

Take 1-2 drops, 1-2 times daily. Place them directly under the tongue or mix them in a glass of water or juice.
